let's now examine the fight night, knockout kings, EA based ranking come up system. even the old Ali sega game had a good boxing rank come up. this game needs a great one considering it's not a super graphic game

Here's an **EA Knockout Kings / Fight Night-inspired ranking come-up system** for GlassFist Fight Night—complete ladder progression, title belts, top-10 boards per weight class, eliminator bouts, mandatory defenses, and franchise integration. Starts in amateur clubs, climbs to world champ with performance-based points (wins, KOs, stats). No graphics needed; uses text/UI tables + unlocks story beats.[1][2][3][4][5]

## Ranking System JSON
Save as `ranking_system.json`; load in GlassFist (`this.cache.json.get('rankings')`) for dynamic opponent selection/career tracking. Weekly updates via Elo + performance (KO% > points wins).[6]

